lancer a.", "words": [55, 56]}, {"id": 14, "text": "s'asseoir 2.", "words": [57, 58]}, {"id": 15, "text": "entrer b.", "words": [59, 60]}, {"id": 16, "text": "enlever 3.", "words": [61, 62]}, {"id": 17, "text": "être debout c.", "words": [63, 64, 65]}, {"id": 18, "text": "sortir", "words": [66]}, {"id": 19, "text": "4.", "words": [67]}, {"id": 20, "text": "se lever d.", "words": [68, 69, 70]}, {"id": 21, "text": "être assis 5.", "words": [71, 72, 73]}, {"id": 22, "text": "mettre e.", "words": [74, 75]}, {"id": 23, "text": "attraper", "words": [76]}, {"id": 24, "text": "Complétez par les mots suivants.", "words": [77, 78, 79, 80, 81]}, {"id": 25, "text": "emmène — pose lance -— apporte - sort - enlève - entre", "words": [82, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87, 88, 89, 90, 91, 92, 93]}, {"id": 26, "text": "1.", "words": [94]}, {"id": 27, "text": "Adeline une bouteille de vin sur la table.", "words": [95, 96, 97, 98, 99, 100, 101, 102]}, {"id": 28, "text": "2.", "words": [103]}, {"id": 29, "text": "Sandrine dans le magasin pour acheter un stylo.", "words": [104, 105, 106, 107, 108, 109, 110, 111]}, {"id": 30, "text": "3.", "words": [112]}, {"id": 31, "text": "Simon du bureau à 18h.", "words": [113, 114, 115, 116, 117]}, {"id": 32, "text": "4.", "words": [118]}, {"id": 33, "text": "Michel ses enfants au cinéma.", "words": [119, 120, 121, 122, 123]}, {"id": 34, "text": "5.", "words": [124]}, {"id": 35, "text": "Louis le livre de la table.", "words": [125, 126, 127, 128, 129, 130]}, {"id": 36, "text": "6.", "words": [131]}, {"id": 37, "text": "Étienne un ballon à la petite fille.", "words": [132, 133, 134, 135, 136, 137, 138]}, {"id": 38, "text": "7.", "words": [139]}, {"id": 39, "text": "Bertrand du chocolat à ses amis.", "words": [140, 141, 142, 143, 144, 145]}, {"id": 40, "text": "a Choisissez la ou les bonnes réponses.", "words": [146, 147, 148, 149, 150, 151, 152]}, {"id": 41, "text": "Quelle(s) partie(s) du corps utilise-t-on quand.", "words": [153, 154, 155, 156, 157, 158]}, {"id": 42, "text": "1.", "words": [159]}, {"id": 43, "text": "On court?", "words": [160, 161]}, {"id": 44, "text": "[les jambes | les bras | les pieds 2.", "words": [162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 167, 168, 169, 170]}, {"id": 45, "text": "On tient quelque chose?", "words": [171, 172, 173, 174]}, {"id": 46, "text": "[les mains | les yeux | les doigts | 3.", "words": [175, 176, 177, 178, 179, 180, 181, 182, 183, 184]}, {"id": 47, "text": "On marche?", "words": [185, 186]}, {"id": 48, "text": "4.", "words": [187]}, {"id": 49, "text": "On est assis ?", "words": [188, 189, 190, 191]}, {"id": 50, "text": "[les cheveux | les fesses | les bras | 5.", "words": [192, 193, 194, 195, 196, 197, 198, 199, 200, 201]}, {"id": 51, "text": "On est debout ?", "words": [202, 203, 204, 205]}, {"id": 52, "text": "[le ventre | les jambes", "words": [206, 207, 208, 209, 210]}, {"id": 53, "text": "Tests 55 à 58 k trente-sept + 37", "words": [211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 217, 218]}]}